{"title":"荐歌：说爱你（蔡依林）","slug":"荐歌：说爱你（蔡依林）","date":"2022-03-06T14:24:28.000Z","updated":"2022-03-08T14:46:58.532Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/荐歌：说爱你（蔡依林）.json","excerpt":"文章来自微信公众号“科文路”，欢迎关注、互动。转发须注明出处。今天在随机播放的音乐中听到了《说爱你》（蔡依林），不由自主的就跟着唱了起来。那就用这首回忆曲说个晚安！（原版要会员了=。=）","covers":null,"content":"<blockquote>\n<p>文章来自微信公众号“科文路”，欢迎关注、互动。转发须注明出处。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>今天在随机播放的音乐中听到了《说爱你》（蔡依林），不由自主的就跟着唱了起来。</p>\n<p>那就用这首回忆曲说个晚安！（原版要会员了=。=）</p>\n<iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=330 height=86 src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=406907053&auto=1&height=66\"></iframe>\n\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=a001909akc2\" allowFullScreen=\"true\"></iframe>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">作词 : 梁鸿斌</span><br><span class=\"line\">作曲 : 周杰伦</span><br><span class=\"line\">编曲 : 吕绍淳</span><br><span class=\"line\">我的世界</span><br><span class=\"line\">变得奇妙更难以言喻</span><br><span class=\"line\">还以为是从天而降的梦境</span><br><span class=\"line\">直到确定手的温度来自你心里</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">这一刻我终于勇敢说爱你</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">一开始 我只顾着看你装做不经意</span><br><span class=\"line\">心却飘过去还窃喜</span><br><span class=\"line\">你 没发现我</span><br><span class=\"line\">躲在角落忙着快乐</span><br><span class=\"line\">忙着感动从彼此陌生到熟</span><br><span class=\"line\">会是我们从没想过真爱</span><br><span class=\"line\">到现在 不敢期待</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">要证明自己</span><br><span class=\"line\">曾被你想起 Really</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">我胡思乱想就从今天起</span><br><span class=\"line\">I wish 像一个陷阱</span><br><span class=\"line\">却从未犹豫 相信你真的愿意</span><br><span class=\"line\">就请给我惊喜</span><br><span class=\"line\">关于爱情过去没有异想的结局</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">那天起却颠覆了自己逻辑</span><br><span class=\"line\">直到确定手的温度来自你心里</span><br><span class=\"line\">这一刻也终于勇敢说爱你</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>再看收录该歌曲的《看我72变》这张专辑，下面加粗的这三首歌是不是有点突兀，它们几乎都成了蔡依林身上的符号。没错，因为它们都是周杰伦作曲的。</p>\n<div class=\"table-container\">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>歌曲</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>说爱你</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>看我72变</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>假面的告白</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>奴隶船</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>布拉格广场</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>做一天的你</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Prove It</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>爆米花的味道</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>马甲上的绳索</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>好东西</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>骑士精神</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p>最后再提个冷知识：想必有机会去布拉格的朋友应该都找过这个所谓的布拉格广场，然而发现根本就没这个广场😂。</p>\n<p><strong>都看到这儿了，不如关注每日推送的“科文路”、互动起来~</strong></p>\n","more":"<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=a001909akc2\"